  "YangsThoughts": "The invasion strategies that created the Boyyi also shaped the Canis III. Originally a second-line unit, the Canis was designed to aggressively engage Inner Sphere forces. While its heavy firepower looked good on paper, severe heat problems and lack of speed limited its effectiveness. After the Wars of Reaving, Clan Coyote developed the costly Canis II, producing only a few units. Just before their next invasion, the Coyotes reimagined this workhorse again, resulting in the Canis III, improved for better battlefield performance.",
